<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB08301</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT PROVIDING FOR THE PROTECTION OF FINANCIAL CONSUMERS</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Seeks to recognize the role of financial regulators in ensuring that the rights of each and every consumer are protected.

Provides therefore, among others, financial regulators such as the Bangko Sentral ng Pilipinas, Insurance Commission and the Securities and Exchange Commission, rulemaking, surveillance and inspection, market monitoring, and enforcement powers relative to consumer protection

Defines Investment Adviser as any person who, engages in the business of advising others, as to the value of investment products or as to the advisability of investing in, purchasing, or selling
investment products, or who issues or promulgates analyses or reports concerning investment products, with several exclusions thereon.
</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>ONG, HENRY C.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2018-09-26</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Tambunting (000 2018-10-10)</td><td>2. Sy-Alvarado (000 2018-11-19)</td><tr><td>3. Nieto (000 2018-11-29)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>COMMITEE HEARINGS/ACTIONS:</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp1. Deliberated upon by the Mother Committee on 2018-11-13</b><tr><td colspan=3>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp-1st deliberation. Bill approved with light amendments with respect to concerns of stakeholders , subject to style.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp2. Committee Report filed on 2019-02-07</b><tr><td colspan=3>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp-Committee Report 1211
